      <td style="text-align: left">‚ÄúCopy and repeat exactly what the person who calls this TQ is doing. It‚Äôs a way for the learner to engage with the texture of the language without having to think about what things mean. ‚ÄúCopy what I say and what I do and you‚Äôll figure it out.‚Äù</td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><img src="https://whereareyourkeys.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/full-sentences.gif" alt="" /></td>
    </tr>
