      <td style="text-align: left">This technique lets you say something that you aren‚Äôt sure is correct without working about people jumping on you. ‚ÄúA learner signals Mumble to create a correction-free space when they‚Äôre uncertain about a piece of language.‚Äù</td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><img src="https://whereareyourkeys.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/mumble.gif" alt="" /></td>
