      <td style="text-align: left"><a href="http://whereareyourkeys.org/technique-glossary/#craigslist">Craigslist</a></td>
      <td style="text-align: left">‚ÄúCraigslists are sets of related words that can be practiced together outside of a sentence (e.g., yes/no/maybe or I/you/he/she)‚Ä¶.‚Äù</td>
